**Summary of findings for `context.go`:**

| # | Type | Location | Severity | Description |
|---|------|----------|----------|-------------|
| 1 | QUESTION | context.go:86-92 | Low | `Reset()` uses `[:0]` slicing, retaining old param values in backing arrays of pooled contexts |
| 2 | QUESTION | context.go:100-102 | Low | `URLParam()` has no bounds guard — implicit invariant that `len(Values) >= len(Keys)` |
| 3 | QUESTION | context.go:48-51 | Low | `parentCtx` field is dead code — documented as enabling `context.Context` but interface not implemented, field never read |
