| 5 | BUG | mux.go:88-89 | Medium | `pool.Put(rctx)` not deferred — panics without Recoverer skip Reset/Put, leaking context data |

**Overall: SHIP IT** — no critical or high issues. The medium finding is an interaction concern in mux.go's pool lifecycle, not in context.go itself.
